data.description: It doesnt get any better. Super location, plenty of sq ft & updated too. Enjoy granite kitchen, ceramic tile. Beautiful cherry cabinetry. 3 full baths, including master bath. Walk out basement, patio, deck & pond. Extra storage, large garage & a view of the lake that will start your day off with sunshine & smile.
data.whatILove: You want to stay in Lake Orion and you are looking for a newer home.  Granite counter tops and a big kitchen are high on your list.  No sharing baths in this house... there are three full ones.  You want to feel like you are home to relax and the view here is as serene as it can be with a picture window to a full view of the lake.  Come home!
